'''玉冰燒'''又名肉冰燒，是[[廣東|廣東]]的一種[[米酒|米酒]]，為廣東十大名酒之一<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.sina.com.tw/article/20130701/10032132.html |title=廣東十大名酒「玉冰燒」供不應求 |access-date=2017-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170922060004/http://news.sina.com.tw/article/20130701/10032132.html |archive-date=2017-09-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，屬小麹[[兼香型白酒|兼香型白酒]]，又可进一步再细分为豉香型白酒。在[[釀造|釀造]]米酒的過程中加入肥[[豬肉|豬肉]]泡浸，令酒質更醇和。玉冰烧是佛山地区的酒，记载于《熙宁酒课》。

傳說是由清末[[佛山|佛山]][[石湾镇街道|石灣]]陳太吉酒苑第三代東主、[[石灣酒廠|石灣酒廠]]創始人[[陳如岳|陳如岳]]所創「肥肉釀浸，缸埕陳藏」的釀造工藝<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://mingpaomonthly.com/%E7%8E%89%E5%86%B0%E7%87%92%E5%92%8C%E7%8E%AB%E7%91%B0%E9%9C%B2%E3%80%80%EF%BC%88%E5%8A%89%E8%87%B4%E6%96%B0%EF%BC%89/ |title=玉冰燒和玫瑰露 |access-date=2017-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180412034946/http://mingpaomonthly.com/%E7%8E%89%E5%86%B0%E7%87%92%E5%92%8C%E7%8E%AB%E7%91%B0%E9%9C%B2%E3%80%80%EF%BC%88%E5%8A%89%E8%87%B4%E6%96%B0%EF%BC%89/ |archive-date=2018-04-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/food/2005-09/01/content_3428558.htm |title=廣東米酒玉冰燒的由來 |accessdate=2017-02-22 |archive-date=2010-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101205025709/http://news.xinhuanet.com/food/2005-09/01/content_3428558.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

